channel.title: ProjectAmbrotos
channel.description:
Hello all. I've decided to make a new called ProjectNero. Now I know how to code and all that stuff I just cant carry all the weight, I do need a Co-owner that actually knows what he's doing. I'll list all the positions at the bottom of this post. I will be asking for the co-owner to pitch in every month but only like 1/3 of the vps. So if you would like to help me create this or are interested in the positions please add my Skype.
This is a 317/PI server!
My Skype- XxGreenDotxX
Positions Available
1- Co-owner(Needs to know how to code) 2- Website developer 3- Possibly a beta tester.
